Configuration File
====================

Some variables in the configuration file have been replaced by others:

  Before            Now
  ---------------   -------------------
  debug             log-level


Scripts
====================

The "icms-start.py" and "icms-start-server.py" scripts do not accept the
"debug" parameter anymore.


Update the database
====================

As usual instances must be updated following the standard procedure:

  1. Make a backup

  2. Update the database:

     $ icms-update.py xxx

  3. Rebuild the catalog:

     $ icms-update-catalog.py xxx


